name: PONGA DO PASSINHO #TECHNOBREGA
description: In the early hours of the morning in the Amazonian city of Belem, Brazil a dockside warehouse is shaking to the sound of tecnobrega. The TREME dance sums up well what we are. It's strong, free, easy, mixed. It's a little heavy metal, a little gay, a little black. Everybody dance. It takes a lot of attitude to get out there shaking. And this is Ponga do Passinho, one of the kings of Tremidinha. Kambo, 2021. Amaz√¥nia, Brasil. IG @kambo.art
